# Code of conduct

All projects under <https://github.com/urothis> adopt the Rust Code of Conduct. Everyone is held to the same standard of conduct when interacting in these repositories as if they were rust-lang repositories.
Enforcement

Please contact @urothis at <urothis@gmail.com> or discord, to call attention to code of conduct violations.

Note that while we elect to follow the Rust Code of Conduct, this is not an official Rust venue, and consequently enforcement of the code of conduct in these repositories is not the responsibility of the Rust moderation team.
